<div id="comments" class="comment-list hot show">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="670462521">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-670462521" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-670462521" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="670462521">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/manalindros/">Hanzie</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-05-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">近期很警惕买专栏文集。因为没有多大知识意义。它们通常零散而不统一，缺乏一个思想体系，大多是作者定时被逼交稿的口水产物。但梁先生的就是不一样，他就是能把平常事说出一套知识体系，把残酷真相说得叫人如沐春风</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1015571628">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1015571628" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1015571628" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1015571628">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
